verbose_text: Simultaneous co-application of IL-1beta with mechanical loading in the form of CTS, completely blocked the effect of IL-1beta, causing no statistically significant differences between IL-1beta treatment and untreated controls for both NO [P = 0.545, XREF_FIG (A)] and PGE 2 [P = 0.290, XREF_FIG (B)].
